    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="section">数据</h3>
<p>最近有一个项目，有一个表数据结构如下</p>

<table class="table">
<thead>
<tr>
  <td>name</td>
  <td>description</td>
  <td> technique_id </td>
  <td>references_count</td>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
  <td>name_1</td>
  <td>description</td>
  <td>1</td>
  <td>5</td>
</tr>

<tr>
  <td>name_2</td>
  <td>description</td>
  <td>2</td>
  <td>4</td>
</tr>

<tr>
  <td>name_3</td>
